## 🚀 Features
- Two-stage semantic filtering for retrieval augmentation.  
- Conflict-free fusion mechanism for multi-source evidence.  
- Self-assessment module to estimate retrieval correctness.  
- Support for BEIR-style retrieval benchmarks and PoisonedRAG attack evaluation.

